{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, our CPMI-ChatGLM model markedly enhances the usability of knowledge while ensuring the security and fluency of the results.",
    "We developed CPMI-ChatGLM by fine-tuning ChatGLM-6B using the PEFT approach.",
    "Despite having only 6.2 billion parameters, ChatGLM-6B still performs consistently with human preferences.",
    "The detailed hyperparameter information for fine-tuning ChatGLM-6B using the LoRA algorithm and P-Tuning v2, as well as the specific hyperparameter details for other comparative models, are provided below:",
    "For LoRA fine-tuning, we conducted fine-tuning for 5 h on two RTX 3090Ti (24 GB) GPUs."
  ]
}